  "The vertex is at t = −40/(2·(−8)) = 2.5, and h(2.5) = −8(6.25) + 40(2.5) + 3 = −50 + 100 + 3 = 53 feet.": "顶部为 t =-40/(2-(8)) = 2.5, h(2.5) = -8(6.25) + 40(2.5) + 3 =- 50 + 100 + 3 = 53英尺。",
  "A company's monthly revenue data forms an inverted U. Quadratic regression gives R = −50x² + 800x + 1000, where x is months since launch. What is the predicted maximum revenue?": "公司的月收入数据构成逆向U. Quadratic回归值为 R =- 50x2 + 800x + 1000, 其中x 是发射后几个月。预计的最大收入是多少?",
  "The vertex is at x = −800/(2·(−50)) = 8, and R(8) = −50(64) + 800(8) + 1000 = −3200 + 6400 + 1000 = $4,200.": "顶点为x=-800/(2-(50)=8;R(8)=-50(64)+800(8)+1000=-3200+6400+1000=4 200。",
  "A roller coaster designer uses quadratic regression on height data and gets h = 0.5d² − 10d + 80, where d is distance in meters. What is the lowest height of the track?": "过山海岸设计师在高度数据上使用二次回归,然后得到 h = 0.5d2 = 10d + 80, d 是米的距离。轨道的最低高度是多少?",
  "The vertex is at d = −(−10)/(2·0.5) = 10, and h(10) = 0.5(100) − 10(10) + 80 = 50 − 100 + 80 = 30 meters.": "顶部为d=-(-10)/(2-0.5)=10和h(10)=0.5(100)-10(10)+80=50-100+80=30米。",
  "A farmer records crop yield versus rainfall. The regression model is Y = −5r² + 60r + 100, where r is rainfall in inches. If there are 8 inches of rain, what is the predicted yield?": "农民记录作物产量和降雨量。回归模型是Y = - 5r2 + 60r + 100,雨量以英寸计。如果有8英寸的降雨,预测产量是多少?",
  "Substituting r = 8: Y = −5(64) + 60(8) + 100 = −320 + 480 + 100 = 260 bushels.": "替代r=8:Y=-5(64)+60(8)+100=-320+480+100=260桶。",
  "A baseball player's batting average over 10 seasons shows data that curves upward then downward. Using quadratic regression, the model is y = −0.003x² + 0.04x + 0.200. In which season does the player peak?": "棒球手在10个赛季中平均打球, 显示向上然后向下曲线的数据。 使用二次回归, 模型是 y = - 0.003x2 + 0.04x + 0. 200。 玩家在哪个赛季会达到峰值 ?",
  "The vertex is at x = −0.04/(2·(−0.003)) = 0.04/0.006 ≈ 6.67, so the player peaks around season 7 (rounding to the nearest whole season).": "顶点为 x = - 0.04/ (2- (-0.003) = 0.04/ 0.006  6. 67, 因此玩家在第七季前后会达到峰值( 圆到最近的整个季节 )。",
  "A sprinkler's water coverage area was measured at different pressure settings. Regression gives A = −0.1p² + 4p + 10, where p is pressure in psi and A is area in ft². If the sprinkler operates at 15 psi, what area is predicted?": "喷洒器的水覆盖面积在不同的压力设置下测量。 递减给 A = = 0.1p2 + 4p + 10, p 是 psi 的压力, A 是 ft2 的面积。 如果喷洒器在 15 psi 操作, 预测的面积是多少 ?",
  "Substituting p = 15: A = −0.1(225) + 4(15) + 10 = −22.5 + 60 + 10 = 47.5 ft².": "替代p=15:A=-0.1(225)+4(15)+10=-22.5+60+10=47.5平方英尺。",
  "A student finds a quadratic regression for test scores versus hours studied: S = −2h² + 28h + 10. The R² value is 0.89. The student predicts the score for 20 hours of studying. Is this prediction reliable?": "学生发现测试分数和学习时数的二次回归:S=-2h2+28h+10。R2值为0.89。学生预测得分为学习20小时。这一预测是否可靠?",
  "Extrapolating to h = 20 gives a negative score (−230), which is impossible, demonstrating that quadratic models can produce unrealistic predictions outside the original data range.": "以h = 20推算得出负分(-230),这是不可能做到的,表明二次模型可以产生不切实际的预测,超出原始数据范围。"
